oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 11
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part eleven of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is twenty-five of an unidentified number of tapes.
